Game sequence:
1. Setup board
  a) Make players
  b) Make board - divide board into regions
  c) Make pieces

2. Decide on first player
  a) Randomly decide which player is to go first
  b) Player 1 takes black (or X) and player 2 takes white (or O)

3. Turn
  a) Player places piece into empty section
  b) Check if player has won
  c) Choose a region to turn (1, 2, 3 or 4)
  d) Choose a direction to turn said region
  e) Turn said region in chosen direction
  f) Check is player has won
  g) Pass turn to next player
  h) Repeat turn sequence
